  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "If Instantsearch were able to load previous pages by setting, with a max. that can be overwritten, it would be very flexible for the developers using the library to determine themselves wether or not it would break their implementation.\r\n\r\nSo basically two settings to instantsearch:\r\n- loadPreviousPagesOnReload: [boolean=false]\r\n- loadPrevioudPagesLimit: [integer=2]\r\n\r\nThis would be no more breakable than overwriting the hitsPerPage to a high number. \r\n\r\n",
